{"type":"message","id":"a41241f1","parentId":"91f47ae4","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:00:23.145Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"命令不支持这个用法。让我尝试其他方法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:54","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw clawhub search tavily 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:55","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:56","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw clawhub install tavily-search 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:57","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw --help 2>&1 | findstr -i \"skill\\|install\\|clawhub\" || openclaw --help 2>&1 | Select-String -Pattern \"skill|install|clawhub\" -CaseSensitive:$false"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:58","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/AppData/Roaming/npm/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:59","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/LWS/.openclaw/skills/tavily-search/SKILL.md","content":"---\nname: tavily-search\ndescription: Tavily专业搜索引擎集成，提供高质量的网页搜索、新闻搜索、学术搜索功能。支持深度搜索、结果摘要、来源引用。当用户需要搜索最新信息、事实核查、查找资料时使用。\n---\n\n# Tavily Search 搜索引擎技能\n\n## 核心功能\n- 🔍 **网页搜索**：高质量全网搜索，返回最新、最相关的结果\n- 📰 **新闻搜索**：专门搜索最新新闻资讯，支持按时间范围过滤\n- 🎓 **学术搜索**：搜索学术论文、研究报告、专业资料\n- 📝 **智能摘要**：自动生成搜索结果的摘要，节省阅读时间\n- 📌 **来源引用**：所有结果都带原始来源链接，方便核实\n- 🌍 **多语言支持**：支持中英等多种语言搜索\n\n## 配置方法\n在配置文件中添加你的Tavily API Key：\n```yaml\ntavily:\n  api_key: \"your-tavily-api-key\"\n  max_results: 5  # 默认返回结果数量\n  search_depth: \"basic\"  # basic/advanced\n```\n\n## 使用示例\n```python\nfrom tavily import TavilyClient\ntavily = TavilyClient(api_key=\"your-api-key\")\nresponse = tavily.search(\"最新的AI技术发展趋势\", search_depth=\"advanced\")\nprint(response['answer'])  # 自动生成的摘要答案\nprint(response['results']) # 详细搜索结果列表\n```\n\n## 触发场景\n- 用户需要搜索最新的信息、新闻、资料\n- 需要事实核查、验证信息准确性\n- 查找专业知识、学术论文、技术文档\n- 需要获取带来源引用的可靠信息\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:60","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/LWS/.openclaw/skills/tavily-search/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:61","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\skills\\tavily-search\" -Recurse | Select-Object FullName, Length"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:62","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/tavily-search"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:63","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport os\nskill_dir = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/skills/tavily-search')\nprint('Skill directory:', skill_dir)\nprint('Exists:', os.path.exists(skill_dir))\nif os.path.exists(skill_dir):\n    files = os.listdir(skill_dir)\n    print('Files:', files)\n    for f in files:\n        full_path = os.path.join(skill_dir, f)\n        if os.path.isfile(full_path):\n            with open(full_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as file:\n                content = file.read()\n                print(f'SKILL.md content preview: {content[:200]}...')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774090734157}}
